<title>USA: Celestial Seasonings names president/CEO.</title>
<headline>Celestial Seasonings names president/CEO.</headline>
<dateline>BOULDER, Colo. 1997-06-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Celestial Seasonings Inc said Wednesday it has appointed Steve Hughes to be its president and chief executive officer.</p>
<p>Hughes, 42, was formerly executive vice president and general manager of Tropicana/Dole USA, a division of Joseph E. Seagram and Sons.</p>
<p>He replaces Mo Siegel, founder of the company, as president and CEO. Siegel will continue to be chairman, the company said.</p>
<p>Before his job at Seagram's, Hughes was executive vice president and general manager of Healthy Choice, a division of ConAgra.</p>
<p>Celestial Seasonings produces and markets specialty hot teas in the United States.</p>
